name: I Am Where / Luba / I
description:
Portrait of Luba, 1st part of triptych.
 
From the project "I am where"
The project about "Touched out syndrome" and motherhood.
Luba said: I am where is the place my children don't touch anymore. Where the power and the pain are.

3822x5028 px
Photograph by Katya Kanke, 2021
